# The Slavery Hack: Simple Legal Definitions

## 1. Abandoned property
Something that someone left behind and doesn’t want anymore.

## 2. Abeyance
When something (like a decision or property) is waiting for someone to claim it or decide what to do with it.

## 3. Anti-chresis
A special agreement where someone uses property as a promise to pay back a loan, but the lender can use the property while waiting for the money.

